{"tid":757914,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"法律問題 撞死左個衝紅燈嘅行人係司機有罪？","createTime":"2018-07-27T08:32:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T09:39:45.000Z","uid":97503,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"be12a8297890346d376ff6fb246245e94cf37516","tid":757914,"uid":97503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T08:32:26.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇到隔離個po先諗到<br />\n假設個衝紅燈嘅人係喺架車就到佢面前先衝出去，咁個司機一定避唔到架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁撚樣都係司機錯？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加上司機部車比個行人咁撞一撞花咗，有冇得叫死者家屬賠償<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"608e2c920cc40c02c344a50a5e95d12540175dae","tid":757914,"uid":112300,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T08:36:31.000Z","msg":"未聽過地鐵火車車死人要坐監"},{"pid":"625a2e2fc2b59062b132da4095227623c2855a24","tid":757914,"uid":5081,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T08:36:37.000Z","msg":"就算係咩情況下, 你都應該見到個行人衝出黎啦<br />\n咁都唔剎制?"},{"pid":"98a0c55a04a516c7a21df5fa1197a31a339e81ae","tid":757914,"uid":60538,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"be12a8297890346d376ff6fb246245e94cf37516","tid":757914,"uid":97503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T08:32:26.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇到隔離個po先諗到<br />\n假設個衝紅燈嘅人係喺架車就到佢面前先衝出去，咁個司機一定避唔到架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁撚樣都係司機錯？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加上司機部車比個行人咁撞一撞花咗，有冇得叫死者家屬賠償<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T08:37:30.000Z","msg":"睇你就知車牌都無<br />\n要睇動機<br />\n去到行人路本身已經要行得慢兼兩頭睇 (理論上)<br />\n如果你係司機無咁做<br />\n車死人一樣有責任"},{"pid":"4aae53acf9b921f2cae35c85895a5bb780a8c90b","tid":757914,"uid":5081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T08:38:12.000Z","msg":"留返比個官判啦<br />\n比你係呢到講羸連登仔又點"},{"pid":"1930deae8657104daab0271f51a0f8efdcfc0135","tid